title: Bumbu Bali 1
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Beer/Wine, Indonesian, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Can do a vegetarian or vegan banquet which includes desserts. Outdoor restaurant; best to make a reservation. Offers a car service to pick you up and drop you off. Vegans need to specify no eggs. Uses only fresh ingredients. Staff speaks English.
streetAddress: Jalan Pratama, Tanjung Benoa, Nusa Dua
